                     <interp inst="t17910413-8-off38" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17910413-8-off38" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17910413-8-cd39" type="crimeDate">2d of April</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17910413-8-off38 t17910413-8-cd39"></join>, a watch, with the inside case and the outside case made of gold, value 8 l. a silk ribbon, value 1 d. a metal key, value 1 d. a steel bed-hook, value 6 d. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17910413-8-victim140" type="victimName">
                           William 
